{"tid":247991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打試過包皮發炎","createTime":"2017-05-18T08:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T00:28:35.000Z","uid":32445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ab002b156d4d7f4d8d53781b3e7695876aebf461","tid":247991,"uid":32445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:20:30.000Z","msg":"小弟本身未扯果陣好易就反到包皮, 扯咗就反到一半, 應該算包皮口窄<br />\n話說早排打飛機太用力搞到包皮口有d撕裂咗嘅小傷口<br />\n可能清潔得唔好 過兩日發炎<br />\n屙尿係痛到企唔穩<br />\n過咗兩個半禮拜左右到而家已經好返冇再痛, 傷口都埋返口<br />\n諗住差唔多20日冇反包皮黎洗諗住洗下啦<br />\n點知而家反極都反唔到, 反果陣仲有d覺得緊緊地果種痛<br />\n有冇巴打試過發炎好返之後包皮變緊咗<br />\n可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔想割包皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30230a60b827694d1c6f8663f4d3a2254ec4c294","tid":247991,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:23:36.000Z","msg":"呢度係連登診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己經驗就破處直接反埋包皮快靚正"},{"pid":"70a7193ecde5ff565334a0bbc467e8eeb4dbd2c2","tid":247991,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度係連登診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己經驗就破處直接反埋包皮快靚正</blockquote><br />\n皮都脫埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc83b0da652e81f8e01da3ddacafe73923562a2","tid":247991,"uid":29898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:25:06.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"2a6ee3ebb112a4501cd2c937188331ec59704bc4","tid":247991,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:26:47.000Z","msg":"up張圖嚟睇睇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9